      "content": "thanks for the breakdown. that makes sense about the timeout and the variable error. \n\none thing that's weird is that even when we fixed the NameError, we're still getting these random, non-deterministic spikes in latency and occasional 500s that don't always show up in the logs clearly. it's like the system just behaves inconsistently for no reason sometimes. is there any reason why a backend would act so sporadically like that?",
